      <h2>How We Tested These Sea Moss Gummies</h2>

      <div class="tested-box">
        <h3>Our 5-Step Testing Process</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Independent Purchase:</strong> Every product was purchased at full retail price from Amazon or the brand's official website. We do not accept free samples or sponsored placements. This ensures our reviews remain completely independent.</li>
          <li><strong>Ingredient Verification:</strong> Our registered dietitian reviewed each product's Supplement Facts label against clinical research, checking that sea moss doses match label claims, additional ingredients are present in meaningful amounts, and no undisclosed ingredients are listed.</li>
          <li><strong>Third-Party Testing Review:</strong> We contacted each brand to request their Certificate of Analysis (COA) from independent testing labs. We verified testing for heavy metals (lead, arsenic, mercury, cadmium), microbial contamination, and ingredient identity and potency.</li>
          <li><strong>Taste and Texture Evaluation:</strong> A panel of four testers evaluated each gummy for flavor quality, aftertaste, texture, chewability, and overall palatability. Products were scored on a 1-10 scale and tasted blind to eliminate brand bias.</li>
          <li><strong>Value Analysis:</strong> We calculated the true cost per serving for each product, factoring in the number of gummies per bottle, recommended daily dose, available subscription discounts, and per-milligram cost of active sea moss to determine which products deliver the best value.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

